Release 0.3 (2009/11/07)
========================

* Add FileObserver adapter on Python2 and Python3.

* Add Intervaltimer adapter on Python2 and Python3.

* Add wxPython adapter on Python2

* Bugfix: #1 can't install via tarball

Release 0.2 (2009/10/02)
========================

* Add Inter-process communication feature on Python2 and Python3.

* Add Growl adapter on Python2 and Python3.

Release 0.1 (2009/09/05)
========================

* Basic communication features on Python2, Python3, Ruby.